    <item>
      <title>中国承诺增加开发商贷款以应对房屋销售下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/china-pledges-to-boost-developer-lending-as-home-sales-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国要求地方政府更好地支持开发商的融资需求，包括起草一份符合融资条件的项目清单，以遏制房地产市场的长期低迷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/china-pledges-to-boost-developer-lending-as-home-sales-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 12:59:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着利润大幅下滑，美国银行债券交易员的业绩出现意外下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/bofa-bond-traders-post-surprise-drop-as-profit-slumps-by-half</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行(Bank of America Corp.)的盈利未达到预期，因为该行第四季度的众多费用削减了利润，而且该公司的固定收益交易员的收入意外下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/bofa-bond-traders-post-surprise-drop-as-profit-slumps-by-half</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 12:04:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>打击胡塞武装增加中东风险，油价突破 80 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-12</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国及其盟国对也门胡塞叛军发动空袭，以报复红海船只遭受袭击，这些袭击危及了通过重要水道的燃料和货物流动，油价大幅上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-12</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 23:02:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
